      • getNamedClass

        public Class<?> getNamedClass(String name,
                              ClassLoader classLoader)
        Resolve the class object of the given name, allowing full package qualification to be omitted for included classes.
        Parameters:
        name - The name for which we wish to find the class object.
        classLoader - The class loader with which to attempt to load the class of the given name. If null, the class loader of the calling class will be used.
        Returns:
        A class object satisfying the given name according to this set of imports.
